// C3: Physical sensing components
instance SwingAngleEncoderArduino : DTDFVocab:SensingComponent [
    base:desc "Swing‑angle encoder mounted on the gantry crane, samples angular position of the load carriage, and outputs data to an Arduino microcontroller."
]

instance AnemometerArduino : DTDFVocab:SensingComponent [
    base:desc "Wind speed sensor mounted on the gantry crane carriage, measures anemometer readings via an Arduino."
]

instance TemperatureSensorRaspberryPiGreenhouse : DTDFVocab:SensingComponent [
    base:desc "Temperature sensor in the greenhouse, powered by Raspberry‑Pi sensor suite, sends data via ActiveMQ."
]

instance HumiditySensorRaspberryPiGreenhouse : DTDFVocab:SensingComponent [
    base:desc "Humidity sensor in the greenhouse, connected to the Raspberry‑Pi and publishes via ActiveMQ."
]

instance CO2SensorRaspberryPiGreenhouse : DTDFVocab:SensingComponent [
    base:desc "CO₂ sensor in greenhouse, sends data via ActiveMQ."
]

instance IndoorAQSensorRaspberryPi : DTDFVocab:SensingComponent [
    base:desc "Indoor air quality sensor suite on Raspberry‑Pi, streams metrics such as O₂, CO₂, temperature, humidity to Azure Data Store."
]

// C4: Physical‑to‑virtual interaction
instance CraneSwingAngleDataTransmitted : DTDFVocab:DataTransmitted [
    DTDFVocab:producedFrom SwingAngleEncoderArduino
]

instance CraneAnemometerDataTransmitted : DTDFVocab:DataTransmitted [
    DTDFVocab:producedFrom AnemometerArduino
]

instance GreenhouseTempDataTransmitted : DTDFVocab:DataTransmitted [
    DTDFVocab:producedFrom TemperatureSensorRaspberryPiGreenhouse
]

instance GreenhouseHumidityDataTransmitted : DTDFVocab:DataTransmitted [
    DTDFVocab:producedFrom HumiditySensorRaspberryPiGreenhouse
]

instance GreenhouseCO2DataTransmitted : DTDFVocab:DataTransmitted [
    DTDFVocab:producedFrom CO2SensorRaspberryPiGreenhouse
]

instance AirQualityAQDataTransmitted : DTDFVocab:DataTransmitted [
    DTDFVocab:producedFrom IndoorAQSensorRaspberryPi
]

// Data descriptions and enablers
instance CraneSwingAngleData : DTDFVocab:Data [
    base:desc "Swing‑angle telemetry from gantry crane, streamed continuously to the twin's database."
    DTDFVocab:fromData CraneSwingAngleDataTransmitted
    DTDFVocab:inputTo GantryLibEnabler, MosquittoMQTTBrokerEnabler, TimescaleDBEnabler
]

instance CraneAnemometerData : DTDFVocab:Data [
    base:desc "Anemometer telemetry measuring wind speed on crane carriage, streamed continuously."
    DTDFVocab:fromData CraneAnemometerDataTransmitted
    DTDFVocab:inputTo GantryLibEnabler, MosquittoMQTTBrokerEnabler, TimescaleDBEnabler
]

instance GreenhouseTemperatureData : DTDFVocab:Data [
    base:desc "Temperature readings from greenhouse, published to twin via ActiveMQ."
    DTDFVocab:fromData GreenhouseTempDataTransmitted
    DTDFVocab:inputTo ActiveMQBrokerEnabler, InfluxDBEnabler
]

instance GreenhouseHumidityData : DTDFVocab:Data [
    base:desc "Humidity readings from greenhouse, published to twin via ActiveMQ."
    DTDFVocab:fromData GreenhouseHumidityDataTransmitted
    DTDFVocab:inputTo ActiveMQBrokerEnabler, InfluxDBEnabler
]

instance GreenhouseCO2Data : DTDFVocab:Data [
    base:desc "CO₂ data from greenhouse sensors, published to twin via ActiveMQ."
    DTDFVocab:fromData GreenhouseCO2DataTransmitted
    DTDFVocab:inputTo ActiveMQBrokerEnabler, InfluxDBEnabler
]

instance AirQualityAQData : DTDFVocab:Data [
    base:desc "Indoor air quality metrics from Raspberry‑Pi, streamed to Azure Data Store."
    DTDFVocab:fromData AirQualityAQDataTransmitted
    DTDFVocab:inputTo AzureDataStoreEnabler
]

// C10: Models
instance GantryKinematicModel : DTDFVocab:Model [
    base:desc "Kinematic model of the lab‑scale gantry crane, encapsulated in gantrylib Python library."
]

instance GreenhouseBehavioralModel : DTDFVocab:Model [
    base:desc "Behavioral computational model representing greenhouse environmental variables synchronized with actual greenhouse dynamics."
]

instance AirQualityAutomationMLModel : DTDFVocab:Model [
    base:desc "AutomationML‑based structural and process model of indoor space for air quality management."
]

// C2: Acting Components
instance LinearActuatorMotorDriverTrolley : DTDFVocab:ActingComponent [
    base:desc "Motor driver controlling horizontal trolley movement on gantry crane, implemented on microcontroller."
]

instance LinearActuatorMotorDriverVertical : DTDFVocab:ActingComponent [
    base:desc "Motor driver controlling vertical actuator for crane, implemented on microcontroller interface."
]

instance FanMotorArduinoGreenhouse : DTDFVocab:ActingComponent [
    base:desc "Fan driver motor in greenhouse, controlled by Arduino controller."
]

instance IrrigationPumpArduinoGreenhouse : DTDFVocab:ActingComponent [
    base:desc "Irrigation pump actuator in greenhouse, driven by Arduino."
]

instance ElectromagnetVentArduinoGreenhouse : DTDFVocab:ActingComponent [
    base:desc "Electromagnet actuator for automated vent closure in greenhouse, controlled by Arduino."
]

instance ElectromagnetVentControlArduinoAirQuality : DTDFVocab:ActingComponent [
    base:desc "Electromagnet controlling vent regulation in air quality management, driven by Arduino."
]

// C11: Enablers
instance GantryLibEnabler : DTDFVocab:Enabler [
    base:desc "Python library gantrylib encapsulating crane's kinematic model and command interface."
    DTDFVocab:enables OptimalControlService, SensorDataValidationService, FaultDetectionService
]

instance MosquittoMQTTBrokerEnabler : DTDFVocab:Enabler [
    base:desc "Mosquitto MQTT broker handling publish/subscribe messaging between devices for crane telemetry."
    DTDFVocab:enables RealTimeVisualizationService
]

instance TimescaleDBEnabler : DTDFVocab:Enabler [
    base:desc "TimescaleDB storing high‑frequency telemetry from the gantry crane."
    DTDFVocab:enables HistoricalDataLoggingService
]

instance GrafanaEnabler : DTDFVocab:Enabler [
    base:desc "Grafana rendering real‑time data visualization dashboards for the crane."
    DTDFVocab:enables RealTimeVisualizationService
]

instance ActiveMQBrokerEnabler : DTDFVocab:Enabler [
    base:desc "ActiveMQ message broker ingesting sensor data for the greenhouse exemplar."
    DTDFVocab:enables DataIngestionService
]

instance InfluxDBEnabler : DTDFVocab:Enabler [
    base:desc "InfluxDB time‑series database storing greenhouse telemetry."
    DTDFVocab:enables DataIngestionService
]

instance AzureDataStoreEnabler : DTDFVocab:Enabler [
    base:desc "Azure-based data store receiving real‑time sensor streams for air quality management."
    DTDFVocab:enables AzureDataIngestionService
]

instance DockerContainerEnabler : DTDFVocab:Enabler [
    base:desc "Docker container providing reproducible deployment for the digital twin."
    DTDFVocab:enables DaemonDeploymentService
]

instance LoggingApplicationEnabler : DTDFVocab:Enabler [
    base:desc "Logging application streaming crane data into the twin's database."
    DTDFVocab:enables HistoricalDataLoggingService
]

// C6: Services
instance OptimalControlService : DTDFVocab:Service [
    base:desc "Optimal control algorithms for gantry crane motion."
    DTDFVocab:provides OptimalControlAction
]

instance HistoricalDataLoggingService : DTDFVocab:Service [
    base:desc "Historical data logging of crane telemetry to TimescaleDB."
    DTDFVocab:provides DataArchiveAction
]

instance RealTimeVisualizationService : DTDFVocab:Service [
    base:desc "Real‑time data visualization dashboards via Grafana."
    DTDFVocab:provides CraneOperationalInsight
]

instance SensorDataValidationService : DTDFVocab:Service [
    base:desc "Validation of sensor data against kinematic model from gantrylib."
    DTDFVocab:provides CraneOperationalInsight
]

instance FaultDetectionService : DTDFVocab:Service [
    base:desc "Fault detection capability based on sensor data and validation."
    DTDFVocab:provides CraneFaultDetectionAction
]

instance DataIngestionService : DTDFVocab:Service [
    base:desc "Ingests greenhouse sensor data from ActiveMQ into InfluxDB."
    DTDFVocab:provides DataIngestionInsight
]

instance AzureDataIngestionService : DTDFVocab:Service [
    base:desc "Ingests air quality sensor data into Azure Data Store."
    DTDFVocab:provides AzureDataIngestionInsight
]

instance DaemonDeploymentService : DTDFVocab:Service [
    base:desc "Deploys all services inside Docker containers for reproducibility."
]

// C17: Insights/Actions
instance OptimalControlAction : DTDFVocab:Action [
    base:desc "Executes optimized control commands for the crane."
    DTDFVocab:IsAutomatic true
]

instance DataArchiveAction : DTDFVocab:Action [
    base:desc "Archives telemetry data to TimescaleDB after ingestion."
    DTDFVocab:IsAutomatic true
]

instance CraneOperationalInsight : DTDFVocab:Insight [
    base:desc "Provides operational status and performance insights for the gantry crane."
]

instance CraneFaultDetectionAction : DTDFVocab:Action [
    base:desc "Triggers fault detection for the gantry crane, automatically if faults are identified."
    DTDFVocab:IsAutomatic true
]

instance DataIngestionInsight : DTDFVocab:Insight [
    base:desc "Insight into data ingestion pipeline health."
]

instance AzureDataIngestionInsight : DTDFVocab:Insight [
    base:desc "Insight into Azure ingestion status."
]

instance FaultHandlerAction : DTDFVocab:Action [
    base:desc "Handles fault detection outcomes by notifying operators."
    DTDFVocab:IsAutomatic false
]

instance GreenhouseOperationalInsight : DTDFVocab:Insight [
    base:desc "Provides operational and environmental insights for the greenhouse exemplar."
]

instance AirQualityStatusInsight : DTDFVocab:Insight [
    base:desc "Real‑time status insight for indoor air quality monitoring."
]

// Environment and system component
instance CraneEnvironment : DTDFVocab:Environment [
    base:contains SwingAngleEncoderArduino, AnemometerArduino, LinearActuatorMotorDriverTrolley, LinearActuatorMotorDriverVertical
]

instance LabScaleGantryCrane : DTDFVocab:Component [
    base:desc "Lab‑scale gantry crane comprising mechanical gantry structure with horizontal trolley, vertical actuator, load carriage, and embedded controller."
]

instance virtual_to_physical_interaction : DTDFVocab:VirtualToPhysical [
    base:desc "Control commands generated by the Digital Twin—such as optimal trajectory points and target positions—are transmitted to the Physical Crane Interface, which forwards them to the crane controllers over a custom Python connection; validation and authentication mechanisms for these commands are not detailed in the document, and feedback is expected to be provided via updated state logs in the TimescaleDB database."
]

instance twinning_time_scale : DTDFVocab:TimeScale [
    base:desc "Sensor data from the physical gantry crane is published over MQTT (Mosquitto) and ingested by the twin into a TimescaleDB time‑series database with millisecond‑level timestamps. The twin’s trajectory generator and simulation services operate continuously, reacting to each inbound MQTT message. No explicit synchronization frequencies, latency bounds, or temporal granularity thresholds are specified in the documentation."
]

instance dt_constellation : DTDFVocab:Constellation [
    base:desc "The twin is composed of six containers: 1) a TimescaleDB database that archives all sensor and simulation data; 2) a Dashboard for real‑time visualization; 3) a Trajectory Generator Service that computes path profiles; 4) a Simulation Service that runs a kinematic model of the gantry; 5) a Continuous Validation Service that compares simulation outputs against live sensor data; and 6) an MQTT Broker that mediates message exchange between the physical system and the twin components. These containers are orchestrated using containerization technology (e.g., Docker) and coordinated by the broker to maintain consistent state across the twin’s services."
]

instance fidelity_and_validity_considerations : DTDFVocab:FidelityConsideration [
    base:desc "The twin implements a Continuous Validation Service that runs in real time alongside physical trajectory execution. For every commanded trajectory, the service intercepts the measured position vector p_meas(t) and the simulated vector p_sim(t), computing the Euclidean distance ‖p_meas(t)–p_sim(t)‖. If the distance exceeds a configurable threshold (default 50 mm) the service raises an alarm, flags the trajectory as invalid, and records the deviation in a Grafana dashboard. The service also aggregates cumulative error statistics over rolling windows, providing a quantified drift metric that feeds back into the model update pipeline. Validation is performed on every trajectory sample, guaranteeing that model fidelity is maintained and that any sensor drift or actuation mismatch is immediately detected and logged for QA."
]

instance dt_technical_connection : DTDFVocab:TechnicalConnection [
    base:desc "The Digital Twin’s internal services communicate through an MQTT broker that signals between the Trajectory Generator Service, Simulation Service, Continuous Validation Service, and Dashboard, while data persistence occurs in a TimescaleDB instance; specific network topology, bandwidth, latency requirements, and security protocols are not described in the document."
]

instance dt_hosting_deployment : DTDFVocab:Deployment [
    base:desc "The system is deployed on a single on‑premise personal computer. Three Docker containers host the TimescaleDB database, the MQTT broker and the Grafana dashboard. The remaining Python applications (Physical Crane Interface, Control Application, Logging Application, Trajectory Generator Service, Simulation Service, Continuous Validation Service) run as additional Docker containers or native services on the same host. This local deployment uses only the PC’s CPU, RAM and disk resources, with no specified scalability or high‑availability mechanisms. The deployment model is single‑node on‑premise, with the database and broker containerised for consistency, while the applications are managed directly or via simple container orchestration on the host."
]